## Validation Checklist

Before publishing ANY post with a URL, verify:

- [ ] **All 5 parameters present** (utm_term optional for organic only)
- [ ] **Lowercase only** — No capital letters in UTM values
- [ ] **No spaces** — Use underscores `_` for spaces
- [ ] **Consistent naming** — Follow the exact format above
- [ ] **URL encoded properly** — Use `&` between parameters
- [ ] **Correct source** — Match the platform and account
- [ ] **Campaign format** — [theme]_[product] with NO date (date goes in utm_content)
- [ ] **utm_content uses date format** — YYYYMMDD_post[N] for organic social posts
- [ ] **Date matches posting date** — Content identifier reflects actual publishing date
- [ ] **Post number correct** — Increments for multiple posts same day (post1, post2, post3)

