## Common Mistakes to Avoid

❌ **Missing UTMs entirely**
```
https://www.stonerise.tech/request-demo
```

❌ **Inconsistent naming**
```
utm_campaign=InvoiceAI (should be: invoice_ai_procurement)
utm_campaign=202602_invoice_ai_procurement (should be: invoice_ai_procurement - no date)
utm_source=LinkedIn (should be: linkedin_michael or linkedin_company)
```

❌ **Using spaces instead of underscores**
```
utm_content=20260203 post1 (should be: 20260203_post1)
```

❌ **Wrong date format**
```
utm_content=week1_post1 (old format - should be: 20260203_post1)
utm_content=feb3_post1 (wrong format - should be: 20260203_post1)
utm_content=03022026_post1 (wrong date order - should be: 20260203_post1)
```

❌ **Missing source account type**
```
utm_source=linkedin (should be: linkedin_michael, linkedin_stelios, or linkedin_company)
```

❌ **Vague campaign names**
```
utm_campaign=february (should be: invoice_ai_procurement or roi_calculator_general)
```

❌ **Including date in campaign**
```
utm_campaign=202602_invoice_ai (should be: invoice_ai_procurement - date goes in utm_content only)
```

