## Template for New Posts

When creating new social posts, use this template:

```markdown
**Post Content Here**

CTA: [Call to action text]

Link: https://www.stonerise.tech/[page]?utm_source=[SOURCE]&utm_medium=[MEDIUM]&utm_campaign=[CAMPAIGN]&utm_content=[CONTENT]

---
UTM Breakdown:
- Source: [platform]_[account]
- Medium: organic_social / paid_social / email / cpc
- Campaign: [theme]_[product] (NO date - e.g., invoice_ai_procurement)
- Content: [YYYYMMDD]_post[N] (e.g., 20260203_post1)

Example:
utm_campaign=invoice_ai_procurement (no date)
utm_content=20260203_post1 (February 3, 2026, first post)
utm_content=20260203_post2 (February 3, 2026, second post)
```

